{"tid":1640003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參議院共和黨領袖 McConnell ‏希望 NBA 可以學習香港人","createTime":"2019-10-08T22:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T11:08:49.000Z","uid":147314,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74ea43123c1fec4fdfe6dff1d3e3e6c9df5019f5","tid":1640003,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:03:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>麥康奈爾稱香港人冒風險捍衛人權冀NBA學習這份勇氣</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2019-10-09 HKT 04:16</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1485055_1_L_20191009054415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1485055_1_L_20191009054415.jpg&h=059526c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">麥康奈爾希望美國NBA可以學習香港人的勇氣，不要放棄價值觀。（美聯社資料圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n美國國會參議院共和黨領袖<span style=\"color: red;\">麥康奈爾</span>在社交專頁說，香港人甘願冒著風險，捍衛他們的言論自由、人權及自治權，認為比金錢利益更重要，他希望美國NBA可以學習這一份勇氣，為了香港人堅持的底線，不要放棄價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n參議院民主黨領袖<span style=\"color: red;\">舒默</span>亦在社交專頁說，與爭取民主權利的香港人，及希望發聲支持香港人的美國人，同一陣線，又說無人可以禁止美國人為自由而發聲。<br />\n<br />\n美國前國務卿希拉莉就在社交專頁說，每一位美國人，都有權發聲支持香港的民主與人權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485055-20191009.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485055-20191009.htm&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=a443fbfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485055-20191009.htm&h=eb6b04c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485055-20191009.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n支豚唔好停 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe525af67561f1bf83660188af7feb413e02b7b","tid":1640003,"uid":147314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/732596482336002049/JYMrr9_4_bigger.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fprofile_images%2F732596482336002049%2FJYMrr9_4_bigger.jpg&h=c856e2bc&s={SIZE}\" />Leader McConnell<br />\n@senatemajldr<br />\n<br />\nThe people of Hong Kong have risked much more than money to defend their freedom of expression, human rights, and autonomy. I hope the <span style=\"color: red;\">@NBA</span> can learn from that courage and not abandon those values for the sake of their bottom line.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1181557253075288066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1181557253075288066&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=ee0b4d3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1181557253075288066&h=4f24aaac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1181557253075288066</a>"},{"pid":"969630946f2881ff5daaddbe18a2560cc4c4fdef","tid":1640003,"uid":75232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:07:05.000Z","msg":"Moscow Mitch <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529d66cb8d81e49ee5b0b8a2a7b1107ce3af8ae0","tid":1640003,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e33d9b671bdc83f49ba4c8d292d8e0b4df5f6d5","tid":1640003,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:17:47.000Z","msg":"大家快d 幫手入去like / RT下"},{"pid":"5de94cf95e5e42e47e2495261f41acea9566182e","tid":1640003,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote